   "options": "<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"background-color: #f8f9fa;\">\n<th style=\"width: 15%;\">RATING</th>\n<th style=\"width: 10%;\">SCORE</th>\n<th>DEFINITION</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Outstanding</strong></td>\n<td><strong>5</strong></td>\n<td>Exceptional achievement clearly demonstrating outstanding initiative, creativity and/or results.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Excellent</strong></td>\n<td><strong>4</strong></td>\n<td>Consistently meets the standards and exceeds the requirements of the job in MOST aspects.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Good</strong></td>\n<td><strong>3</strong></td>\n<td>Normal standard of performance expectation. Fully meets the requirements of the job.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Fair</strong></td>\n<td><strong>2</strong></td>\n<td>Performance generally falls short of the expected standard. Improvement needed. Monthly review for 3 months.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Poor</strong></td>\n<td><strong>1</strong></td>\n<td>Inferior and unacceptable performance. Failure to meet basic job requirements.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"
